OL,3,GWales
OL,4,
OL,5,CThis Evening and Tonight:FSome showers
OL,6,Fcontinuing this evening overnight,
OL,7,Fthese most frequent in the west but
OL,8,Fpushing further inland overnight.
OL,9,FOtherwise, mostly cloudy with
OL,10,Foccasional clear spells allowing
OL,11,Ftemperatures to dip away.
OL,12,
OL,13,CThursday:FOften cloudy with a
OL,14,Fscattering of showers throughout the
OL,15,Fday. Occasional bright or sunny breaks
OL,16,Fdeveloping through the day with light
OL,17,Fwinds.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
OL,24,ANext Page  BWeather  CReg News  FReg TV
