OL,4,
OL,5,COutlook for Friday to Sunday:FShowers,
OL,6,Fheavy at times, likely on Friday mixed
OL,7,Fwith sunny intervals. Some rain
OL,8,Fpossible on Saturday then drier on
OL,9,FSunday. Turning warmer after chilly
OL,10,Fnights at first.
OL,23,QppppppppppppppppppppGSource: Met Office
